column5: Happy Double Belated Pete!!
Quite a crop of them today! Have a great day Pete. I know it was yesterday   but I thought I'D JUST TALK LOUDLY FOR YOU TODAY!!!!!!!!!!
Happy Birthday, Pete.  Best Fishes too.
Happy B-day Pete !!
Hope yer day is going great Pete. Happy b-day.
Happy b-day neighbour.
Happy Birthday Pete. Hope you having a great day.
Have a good one Sweet Pete!!!!!  HappyBirthday bud.  Joey

Hmmmmm, what's this all about Pete.....you phone me yesterday just to shoot the bull and you don't even tell me it's your B-Day ??  Guess you didn't want to share your cake with your favorite net man eh ??  Oh well, Happy Birthday anyways bud and I'll see you in 2 weeks !!!!  All the best to you Pete !!!!
Hope you had a great day Pete...and like Lew thanks for the PM chat without sharing your cake as well! LOL
All th best Peter. Looking forward to seeing you May 24. Hope you catch something this year. LOL Ed
Hey Pete, hope you had a great day...  Maureen
Happy belated Neighbour!  I'll have a cold one for you tonight during the game.  Tony
Sorry I'm late, but happy B day  John
Happy Bday!!!
All the "Best" to you on this day and many many more to ya........
hey Pete is your boat water-ready yet? hope to see ya out for some sliver soon - have a swell day!
Happy Birthday Pete!  Whopper
Happy Birthday Bud I hope you got what you deserved.......( new Boat I am sure)   Art
just 16 days till ya can celibrate in style spending $$$$$$ on new musky gear happy Bday Pete have a good one
Happy BD big guy! Drop me a line...its almost time!!! ;-)
Happy Birthday Squid!  Hope you had a great day!
CAKE !!!...did someone mention...Cake !!!  Hope you had a big slice for me Pete..Happy Birthday !
Happy belated birthday buddy, all the best to you! Hopefully it was a good one.
Happy Birthday Bud all the best to you.  Regards, Sam
Thanks very much everyone. I missed the post yesterday as I was not on line after work, imagine that.
